project.name: eAbsentee
project.description: eAbsentee is an open-source system used to request absentee ballots. eAbsentee is sponsored by Vote Absentee Virginia, a not-for-profit, non-partisan 501(c)4 organization established to help broaden voter access across all parties in Virginia.
